experiment 1: dpg 100 features, sigma=0.5, ~300 iterations -> m*=1.1, s0=pi+-0.01, N=12, alpha=1e-3
experiment 2: dpg 100 features, sigma=0.5,~1000 iterations -> m*=1.2, s0=pi+-0.01, N=100, alpha=1e-3
experiment 3: dpg 100 features, sigma=0.5,~1000 iterations -> invariato, s0=pi+-0.01, N=100, alpha=1e-3
